# WOOFI agent coordination

Read `docs/agents/COORDINATION.md` before substantive work.

- **Dev agent** owns: Firebase, services, hooks, screen logic, responsive layout structure, map, MVP flows
- **UX agent** owns: design tokens, `src/components/ui/*`, visual consistency, Storybook/preview

Do not overwrite the other agent's domain. Before large changes: plan, list files, small commits.

Shared: no mock data, i18n only (es-AR), `npm run typecheck` + `npm run audit:i18n`, git as Giggi Argento.
